NAME
    tickit-hello - Tickit application with hello world.

SYNOPSIS
     tickit-hello [-a horiz_align] [-b bg_color] [-f fg_color] [-h] [-v vert_align] [--version] [message]

DESCRIPTION
    This application is Tickit hello world demo.

    Application could present text string in screen.

ARGUMENTS
    *       "-a horiz_align"

            Horizontal align.

            Possible values are:

            *   left

            *   center (default)

            *   right

    *       "-b bg_color"

            Background color.

            Default value is black.

    *       "-f fg_color"

            Foreground color.

            Default value is green.

    *       "-h"

            Print help.

    *       "-v vert_align"

            Vertical align.

            Possible values are:

            *   top

            *   middle (default)

            *   bottom

    *       "--version"

            Print version of script.

    *       "message"

            Text message to present on screen.

EXAMPLE
     tickit-hello "Hello world!"

